name: Rebirth[WIP]
description:
Can you survive in this new world you have been born into?

HOW TO PLAY?

MOVEMENT - WASD

JUMP - SPACE

ATTACK 1 - LEFT MOUSE BUTTON

ATTACK 2 - RIGHT MOUSE BUTTON

PAUSE MENU - ESCAPE
